detailFilter.filterExpression: ( '0' in ( ?p_Reg_Temp? ) ) OR ( [Regular or Temporary C (C-POS)] in ( ?p_Reg_Temp? ) )
( '0' in ( ?p_Full_Part_Time? ) ) OR ( [Full or Part Time (C-POS)] in ( ?p_Full_Part_Time? ) )
( '0' in ( ?p_Incumbent_Type? ) ) OR ( [Assignment or Appointment Type C (C-JOB)] in ( ?p_Incumbent_Type? ) )
( '0' in ( ?p_Work_Description_Type? ) ) OR ( [Work Description Type C (C-JC)] in ( ?p_Work_Description_Type? ) )
case (?p_Vacant?) when 1 then ( [Last Name (C-EE)] = 'N/A') when 2 then ( [Last Name (C-EE)] <> 'N/A') else ( [Last Name (C-EE)] <> 'N/A' or ( [Last Name (C-EE)] = 'N/A') ) end
